text: Estahban County () is a county in Fars Province in Iran. The capital of the county is Estahban.Gitashenasi Province Atlas of Iran اطلس گیتاشناسی استان‌های ایران At the 2006 census, the county's population was 66,391, in 16,606 families. The county is subdivided into two districts (bakhsh): the Central District and Runiz District. The county has three cities: Estahban, Ij, and Runiz. == References == Category:Estahban County
